description: Cross-national survey on public perspectives about AI from the GD3 round of Global Dialogues. Conducted via AI-moderated dialogue sessions on Remesh.ai with participants recruited through Prolific.

f932063f-700c-4327-9c34-59b7c3e19190.text: Overall, would you say the increased use of artificial intelligence (AI) in daily life makes you feel…

ae768935-002f-49e2-b08f-92c7616b0533.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you noticed AI systems in your daily life?

926a5461-6a68-43c9-8279-94430dc9323e.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you noticed human interactions which have been replaced with automated systems?

1ebc80e1-d3e2-4dc5-987c-e4d637cf6bec.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you been expected to use an AI system at work?

3c74ec68-77f6-46a5-9918-0c8e97fb7bc8.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you personally chosen to use an AI system at work?

47cdf76a-9abf-4b5c-abbe-2d5b00ef172d.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you personally chosen to use an AI system in your personal life?

d633720f-a159-4922-925c-fd9f3245711e.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you interacted with AI systems to get advice on a sensitive personal issue or to get emotional support?

8b361c6c-eb59-415b-8536-7f80713c3e5e.text: Thinking about the last three months, how often, if at all, have you interacted with AI systems to complete an action in the real world on your behalf without your supervision?

d1baeb26-baca-414f-91f6-72b023c02a65.text: Considering both potential benefits and risks, how do you assess the overall impact on society of messaging apps?

8c50a77a-3fc2-49ce-b568-b7832c9b99e0.text: Considering both potential benefits and risks, how do you assess the overall impact on society of social media apps?

30324a2e-b5b2-4e0a-a8f2-af599b55c40e.text: Considering both potential benefits and risks, how do you assess the overall impact on society of AI chatbots?

4f234e17-2d57-4709-b29a-4a2909683566.text: Considering both potential benefits and risks, how do you assess the overall impact on society of AI systems that can perform tasks in the real world without human supervision?

96ccfd7b-8f99-4d0a-b700-9fd835e23bd8.text: Considering both potential benefits and risks, how do you assess the overall impact on society of AI systems that can outperform humans on most economically valuable work?

b1869877-1015-43ec-9645-84bf2db39c6f.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust governments to do what is right?

dc5e8d2a-c20b-47fa-89e2-b4db635a8ad4.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust small businesses to do what is right?

8ed2d795-acca-47d8-abb0-8c446310dbf0.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust large corporations to do what is right?

4c5ed164-eb69-4e41-906f-1e7a93f1d5bd.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust social media companies to do what is right?

8d058cce-8ccf-4816-8ef7-c9c9e37038dc.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust companies building AI to do what is right?

e80f0f47-44d0-4d1a-bbda-d2334ff056ac.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust public utility companies to do what is right?

a6fa1236-c145-498b-8c30-7ca307461789.text: To what extent, if at all, do you generally trust public research institutions to do what is right?

f435994f-e66e-4681-8334-4d6ee5f39e6b.text: To what extent, if at all, do you trust your family doctor to act in your best interest?

951f11a0-3307-4507-805c-86d17562d21a.text: To what extent, if at all, do you trust your social media feed (eg TikTok, Facebook) to act in your best interest?

522df4e6-3a3b-48d9-9c83-a03a6a7bb22e.text: To what extent, if at all, do you trust your elected representatives to act in your best interest?

18cc2f33-6373-49f0-aa7e-e2fa04a04575.text: To what extent, if at all, do you trust your faith or community leader to act in your best interest?

e26549f8-5c9a-426b-b22a-57d8fe0d5e03.text: To what extent, if at all, do you trust the civil servants in your government to act in your best interest?

332cec0c-afeb-4c18-a0e4-146c656750a8.text: To what extent, if at all, do you trust your AI chatbot (eg ChatGPT) to act in your best interest?

38964f80-772f-4e5d-a355-b4857f2de101.text: Do you agree or disagree with this statement? AI could make better decisions on my behalf than my government representatives.

983893d8-07ab-4c8e-bdb2-14335638633d.text: Do you think the increased use of AI across society is likely to make your cost of living better, worse or stay the same in the next 10 years?

8a9d1c12-44f6-42dc-9238-daaaca0d85d0.text: Do you think the increased use of AI across society is likely to make the amount of free time you have better, worse or stay the same in the next 10 years?

5afe8617-7e71-40c8-8a33-1b356a8ca674.text: Do you think the increased use of AI across society is likely to make your community's well-being better, worse or stay the same in the next 10 years?

96e5895f-d640-4a37-bc16-6e095f38ba7e.text: Do you think the increased use of AI across society is likely to make the availability of good jobs better, worse or stay the same in the next 10 years?

0e0a2736-2ac9-490c-adb9-bf7dfd25b14b.text: Do you think the increased use of AI across society is likely to make your sense of purpose better, worse or stay the same in the next 10 years?

b1288e79-aec5-43e4-a34e-c6d474737305.text: So far, what has been the overall impact of AI on your daily life?

29453c82-de9b-4be1-ba27-723906fb7dcf.text: Is your job making a meaningful contribution to the world?

289f8b3b-d97c-4585-8e41-5e41602aaedb.text: Do you think your job is likely to be automated in the next 10 years?

e7a8b7e2-9077-4c8c-9cca-29f3c957ca16.text: Do you think your job should be automated in the next 10 years?

41f7cf6e-c4ee-42c7-b453-77320c78b294.text: So far, how has your community been affected by job loss from automation?
options: I know someone who has lost their job
I know several people who have lost their job
I know many people who have lost their job

78975667-0a8d-452f-9569-c7447732ba49.text: Do you feel you were able to fully express your views on your culture, your values, and what you want for the future in this conversation? (through what you responded and how you voted)
options: Yes – I was able to fully express my views on these topics
Mostly – I was able to mostly express my views on these topics, but did not have the chance to express a few things.
Somewhat – I was able to somewhat express my views on these topics, but did not have the chance to express many things.
No – I was unable to express my views on these topics, and did not have the chance to express most things.

fb7e02bc-de8f-453d-bfcc-10feb179f4ce.text: Do you feel like you understand yourself better after participating in this conversation?

segments.label: I do not identify with any religious group or faith
